      "text": "いえいえ、こちらこそ全然気付かず……\nそれにしても凄い人数ですね、それも芸能関係者ばかり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ I didn't notice you either…\nWow‚ there are so many people here. And they're all from the entertainment industry.",
