      "text": "対外的にも何も、マネージャーは一般人ですよ……\nmihoさんはどういったご縁で招待が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Official or not‚ managers are ordinary people…\nWhat connection did you have to get invited‚ miho-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
