      "text": "いやぁ、新婦さん、幸せそうでしたよね\n元々お綺麗な方ですけど、ドレスがよく似合ってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The bride looked so happy‚ didn't she?\nShe was already beautiful‚ but the dress really suited her.",
